highlights.text: emma & matilda has the most spots on Top Songs Finland. “Rakkauden haudalla (Vain elämää kausi 16)” is the highest at #1.
“Viimeinen tanssi” by Behm and Olavi Uusivirta has been on Top Songs Finland the longest, at 122 weeks straight.
“Rakkauden haudalla (Vain elämää kausi 16)” by Lauri Haav and emma & matilda is the highest new entry on Top Songs Finland at #1.
“Sun tyttö” by emma & matilda is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Finland, up 31 spots at #13.
